<div class="space-y-6">

<div>
<h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">How far in advance should I book a Sheffield removal company?</h3>
<p class="text-gray-700">
It’s best to book your removal company as soon as your moving date is confirmed. During busy periods such as summer, availability can become limited, so booking early helps secure your preferred date.
</p>
</div>

<div>
<h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Do removal companies provide packing materials?</h3>
<p class="text-gray-700">
Yes. Most removal companies provide boxes, packing paper, tape, and protective materials. Some also offer full packing services where their team packs your entire home safely.
</p>
</div>

<div>
<h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Can movers dismantle and reassemble furniture?</h3>
<p class="text-gray-700">
Professional movers can usually dismantle larger furniture items such as beds, wardrobes, and tables to make transportation easier. They can then reassemble them at your new property.
</p>
</div>

<div>
<h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Are my belongings insured during the move?</h3>
<p class="text-gray-700">
Most professional removal companies provide goods-in-transit insurance that covers your belongings while they are being transported. Always confirm the level of cover included before booking.
</p>
</div>

<div>
<h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Do Sheffield removal companies offer storage?</h3>
<p class="text-gray-700">
Yes. Many companies offer secure storage facilities for customers who need short-term or long-term storage during the moving process.
</p>
